      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARROTS (5) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Finished in the minors last time when third (24.91) at Goulburn making it back to back placings. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. One of the contenders. TIGGERLONG SNAKE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Nowra over 520m behind Zipping Cruella (30.33) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings five times from seven attempts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. LUMEAH NANCY (2) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 1.75 lengths (36.58) at Nowra. Capable of going close again. BLUE SWALLOW (8) has strong credentials from this draw.",
